latestIgtvVideos.title: Thailand Highlight Reel
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Finally sharing some of my favorite moments from our recent adventure to Thailand! 🏞 Island hopping, venturing to mountaintop temples and hiking to crystal pools in the middle of the jungle. From endless bowls of steaming Pad Thai, vibrant night bazaars, snorkeling in the most turquoise water I’ve ever seen and mystic jungle temples, this trip was definitely a favorite of 2019!
